We’ve got you covered. Our custom plans are tailored to meet your needs with a dedicated customer growth manager, advanced onboarding and support, and enterprise-level security for your peace of mind.

[Book a demo](https://starshipit.com/book-an-appointment)

Why choose Starshipit?
----------------------

*   **No hidden fees –** We don’t charge per-label fees on top of your carrier rates or monthly plan.
*   **Start shipping today –** Even if you don't have a carrier account.
*   **Ready to go integrations –** Get started with all major carriers and platforms.

[Start 30-day free trial](https://app.starshipit.com/Dashboard/SignUp.aspx)

![Image 54: Danny Hancock](blob:http://localhost/b9a31d3949b1882a09ed2f8508d538f3)

“Starshipit is a global solution for us. I can see all my orders, track any order. All my teams are all using the same platform. Training is easier, because it’s one platform we’re pushing out there. It’s a simple, cost-effective solution because it’s a global solution for us.”

— Danny Hancock, Global Operations Manager, Lorna Jane

![Image 55: Lorna Jane ](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/3b2bdf503992dae274ba952ce90e85a621b1d7c0-765x170.png)

![Image 56: Damien Park-Nielson](blob:http://localhost/b9a31d3949b1882a09ed2f8508d538f3)

“We would have really struggled to scale if it wasn’t for Starshipit. Before using their app, our tech platforms weren’t talking, and we would have had to login to multiple carrier accounts to get orders out the door. Now, all of that is handled automatically, meaning we save 1000s of hours and dollars in fulfilment time."

— Damien Park-Nielson, Head of Operations, MESHKI

![Image 57: MESHKI](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/307c1e7bcf03d7462cc55f5272d4d23a51375665-883x129.png)

*   ![Image 58: Speed up fulfilment](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/63fb610ee2e8feebc1a47d41d602c1774896789c-93x62.svg)
    
    Speed up fulfilment
    
    Manage your sales channels and carriers from one dashboard and set up automations to reduce your manual shipping tasks.
    
*   ![Image 59: Control your shipping costs](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/d38ebb7f78b83be424d022d1f536f3b8e45c6c2a-456x456.png)
    
    Control your shipping costs
    
    Bring your own carrier rates (with no additional fees), create automation rules to pick the cheapest carrier, add margins and show live rates at checkout.
    
*   ![Image 60: Your partner for scale](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/ccac81b04d25f83a64e0fbb75919acf354b70268-651x366.png)
    
    Your partner for scale
    
    Starshipit is your partner for growth with dedicated onboarding and ongoing customer support.
    
*   ![Image 61: Reduce support queries](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/f6ccacd78097cfde2c8c775c809536d16533474a-203x170.png)
    
    Reduce support queries
    
    Send proactive notifications and reduce customer package queries.
    
*   ![Image 62: Cutting-edge shipping software](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/3f6f26dd8f0ab1419abb08953baf2f14a1aa1f29-732x387.png)
    
    Cutting-edge shipping software
    
    Take advantage of new features, products and integrations.
    
*   ![Image 63: Grow internationally](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7kkbpahe/production/c870775c1e25b593962dfd6a4906db203f670880-528x369.png)
    
    Grow internationally
    
    Add international carriers, automate customs documents and enter new markets.
